#. risk identification page. Sections not checked will be shown intially in
#. collapsed mode, but the user can always open those sections with a click."
#: euphorie/content/country.py:50
msgid "help__risk_default_collapsible_sections"
msgstr ""
"Skilgreindu, hvaða upplýsingakaflar ættu að vera sjálfgefnust opnir á síðu "
